"forward-looking" statements within the meaning of Section 27A of the
Securities Act of 1933, as amended, and Section 21E of the Securities Excha=
nge
Act of 1934, as amended, including statements regarding the intent, belief =
or
current expectations of Calpine Corporation ("the Company") and its
